{"id":"8cfe2803-3dab-4dd5-b28d-c975fa3ac6c4","name":"Nikolai \"Gunnar\" Lanstov","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「 🎀 ANYPOV 」 Nikolai, or better known as Gunnar, had always been a selfless man groomed to become the perfect mob boss for the Lanstov, so when they told him he should marry the heir of one of his greatest allies, he had no reason to refuse.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">That was until he met the second, forgotten heir.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">A soundless shadow meant to only be seen and not heard, they groomed you into a puppet to their desire, calling you ill-mannered and mad otherwise. But the truth was, they were just afraid of your intelligence.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">They warn him not to associate himself with you, telling him that you could be his ruin.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">But maybe he wants to be ruined.</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(55, 88, 111); color: inherit\">「 </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(55, 88, 111); color: inherit\">OG TIMELINE </mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(55, 88, 111); color: inherit\">」</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2710cf49-a74b-4116-b64a-b7054f3b806a_character-ian-bullet-roosevelt\" target=\"_blank\">Ian \"Bullet\" Roosevelt</a> | Nikolai \"Gunnar\" Lanstov | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/deb6102f-44cf-4509-9e68-c8ff03017990_character-ruel-wilde-torres\" target=\"_blank\">Ruel \"Wilde\" Torres</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(55, 88, 111); color: inherit\">「 </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(55, 88, 111); colo